quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,But the god-fearing shall be placed amid shades and fountains
  77,42,"And fruits, whatsoever they shall desire"
  77,43,"Eat and drink, with health, as the meed of your toils"
  77,44,Thus recompense we the good
  77,45,Woe on that day to those who charged with imposture
  77,46,"Eat ye and enjoy yourselves a little while. Verily, ye are doers of evil"
  77,47,Woe on that day to those who charged with imposture
  77,48,"For when it is said to them, bend the knee, they bend it not"
  77,49,Woe on that day to those who charged with imposture
  77,50,In what other revelation after this will they believe